item.dc:creator: @Vain1 Vain_
item.description:
@Vain1 wrote:

exactly what i thought. the cache is zipped incorrectly.

the client is downloading this which is incorrectly zipped up.

it’s in the form of RuneMigrantCache_ZIP/RuneMigrantCache/CACHE_INDEXES
when it should be RuneMigrantCache_ZIP/CACHE_INDEXES

instead of right-clicking the cache folder and clicking add to archive, open up the folder (so you can see “Data”, “LOC”, “Mp3”, “Raw”, etc. highlight all those files/folders and then add that to the archive.
